            . I am a perriwig-maker, and live in <placeName id="t17511016-43-crimeloc196">Nightingale lane, Wapping</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17511016-43-crimeloc196" type="placeName" value="Nightingale lane, Wapping"></interp>
